Name: Kitung
Description: A small enthusiastic fighter with a wooden stick. Its determination far exceeds its tiny frame.

Name: Sir Tung
Description: A refined Kitung that has adopted a gentleman's demeanor. Its wand channels focused fighting spirit.

Name: Magi-Tung
Description: A master of both martial arts and mental prowess. Its psychic wand can bend reality itself.

Name: Frigo Camelo
Description: A fridge-bodied camel who wanders aimlessly, embodying surreal melancholy and cursed Italian energy.

Name: Refricamel
Description: Now with proper refrigeration coils, it keeps its cool in deserts and stores snacks for later.

Name: Glacimel
Description: Its freezer core turned cryogenic. It sculpts dune-ice into elegant ridges as it roams.

Name: Twirlina
Description: A tiny cup dancer who practices spins until she's dizzy with delight. Her grace belies her power.

Name: Ballerina Cappuccina
Description: A poised ballerina with a swirling coffee cup for a head. She pirouettes into battle with elegance.

Name: Primarina Ballerina
Description: The cup now forged into steel trim, her grand jet√© leaves shimmering trails. A master of dance and defense.

Name: Frulli Frulla
Description: A jittery coffee-fueled bird with orange glasses. Its caffeine-enhanced reflexes make it hard to catch.

Name: Frulilala
Description: The caffeine finally focuses into static. Its wingbeats crackle as it darts between rooftops.

Name: Frulli Fruletro
Description: A hypercharged flyer that channels thunderstorms through its feathers. It blitzes foes before they can react.

Name: Timmy Cheddar
Description: A young, ambitious rat with big dreams. Still learning the ropes of the underworld but shows great potential.

Name: Tim Cheese
Description: A sharp-dressed humanoid rat who oozes confidence and cunning. Said to run the city's underworld.

Name: Burbaloni Lulliloli
Description: A divine capybara within a coconut, worshipped for its calm yet immense power. Extremely rare.

Name: Chimpanini
Description: A hyperactive jungle prankster that flings seeds and swings through trees with reckless abandon.

Name: Chimpanzini Bananini
Description: Though armless, it hops and rolls through the jungle with surprising speed. Its banana body stores energy from sunlight.

Name: Duckaroo
Description: A cowboy duck that patrols dry plains and dusty canyons, kicking up sand as it chases bandits.

Name: Doggolino
Description: A furious hot-dog spirit. It barks in sizzles and pops, leaving scorch marks where it walks.

Name: Tadbalabu
Description: A little frog-tad that drums on puddles with its tail. Its rhythm attracts other creatures.

Name: Boneca Ambalabu
Description: It grows longer limbs like a doll, keeping a steady jungle rhythm that boosts nearby plants.

Name: Ambalabu Ton-Ton
Description: Stacked like drums, it pounds a beat that spurs seedlings to sprout. Its rhythm can shake the earth.

Name: Abrazard
Description: A small wizard who loves playful mischief. Its spells are mostly harmless, but its psychic power is no joke.

Name: Bolasaeg Selluaim
Description: A creature made entirely of gelatinous ooze. It slowly devours anything in its path with corrosive acid.

Name: Trippi Troppi
Description: A fish that adapted to land but never let go of its aquatic nature. Despite its dopey look, it becomes fierce if provoked.

Name: Il Cacto Hipopotamo
Description: A mysterious fusion of flora and fauna. It thrives in deserts, absorbing sunlight and storing water. Fiercely territorial.

Name: Chicleteira
Description: A humanoid gumball machine that fires sticky gum to trap prey. Its laughter echoes in alleys long after it's gone.

Name: ≈†pijuniro Golubiro
Description: A mechanical pigeon that acts as a covert agent. Its lens-like eyes record everything. It vanishes the moment it's spotted.

Name: Avocadini Guffo
Description: A plump owl with the body of an avocado. Its wings are too small to fly, so it waddles instead. Rich in nutrients.

Name: Bombombini Gusini
Description: A fusion of goose and fighter jet, known for breaking the sound barrier while honking furiously. Extremely aggressive.

Name: Brr Brr Patapim
Description: A peculiar grass creature with extremely thick bark. It moves slowly but can take enormous punishment.

Name: Frycito
Description: Born from a box of superheated fries, Frycito's body crackles with oily flames. It charges into battle with sizzling punches, splattering sparks and crumbs everywhere.

Name: Yoyoi Shaur
Description: A playful yoyo creature that moves by spinning, bouncing, and snapping back into position. Its sunglasses hide faint psychic glows it uses to sense movement around it. When it spins rapidly, it can send out short psychic pulses that disorient opponents.

Name: Yoyoya Shaur
Description: After evolving, its spin becomes perfectly balanced, allowing it to move with incredible precision. It battles with controlled, whip-like motions, predicting attacks before they land. Its shades serve as psychic focus lenses, sharpening its awareness and reactions.

Name: Tralalero Tralala
Description: A mythical three-legged shark wearing fashionable shoes. Said to outswim any creature in existence.
